 src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同VALE比較嘅話<br />\n<br />\n我自己用其他model計咗計估值，VALE應該相對比較低估值啲（平啲）<br />\n不過我睇RIO營收增長會好啲，VALE嚟緊五年預期每年增長係微微負數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知邊隻跑贏<br />\n所以我繼續hold翻熟啲嘅VALE就算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下不是投資建議，純粹個人睇法<br />\n<br />\n<strong>基本面</strong><br />\n<br />\n現價：17.12<br />\n個人估值：<br />\n- 合理位大概 $22<br />\n- bull case $29.幾<br />\n- bear case $20.幾<br />\n<br />\n分析師目標價：<br />\n- 平均值 23.32<br />\n- Median 23.21<br />\n- 最高32.20<br />\n- 最低 16.15<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>技術面</strong><br />\n<br />\n暫定我會呢啲位入貨同take profit，不過都睇到時情況可能改策略<br />\n<br />\n撈貨位：16.19<br />\n- 支撐大概呢個位附近<br />\n<br />\n止賺位：18、20、22 分批走<br />\n- 18前高阻力<br />\n- 20 22係我估值位，唔再高啲先走主要係間公司未來營收增長少少差 唔太有信心<br />\n<br />\n止蝕位：<br />\n- 自己衡量<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1becfdda3b78c4d43e049e0feef73febd68924fd","tid":2471860,"uid":351545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24d22d56138294aec2b945e2111bc572afbae98f","tid":2471860,"uid":258948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T02:20:39.000Z","msg":"RIO BHP VALE呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:54:44.000Z","msg":"巴打出po個時間出得又幾準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b80f7fe7d7997085906779ed0d41842d908d3ae","tid":2471860,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:57:19.000Z","msg":"有fcx&nbsp;(銅金)<br />\n鐵股&nbsp;有間唔中炒下x, tx"},{"pid":"2dc1625cc4d4887a2e86acba2991ad2958f882b4","tid":2471860,"uid":278858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:11:27.000Z","msg":"RIO <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪無新片？"}]}